===音乐===
电影的配乐由[[漢斯·季默|漢斯·季默]]作曲，他是这一系列第二和第三部作品的主要作曲家，也有参与首部作品的音乐创作<ref name="release" />。季默表示他试图在音乐中增加摇滚乐的效果，因为他觉得“海盗就是很多很多年前的摇滚明星”<ref name="video">{{cite web |url=http://www.movieweb.com/movie/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides/hans-zimmer-interview |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides: Hans Zimmer Interview |date=2011-05-05 |publisher=MovieWeb |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120930073953/http://www.movieweb.com/movie/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides/hans-zimmer-interview |archivedate=2012-09-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，他还在片中增加了西班牙元素，并因此与墨西哥[[吉他|吉他]]演奏组合[[罗德里戈和加布里埃拉|罗德里戈和加布里埃拉]]（{{lang|en|Rodrigo y Gabriela}}）和佩内洛普·克鲁兹的弟弟爱德华多（{{lang|en|Eduardo}}）合作，后者创作了片中的一首[[探戈|探戈]]舞曲<ref name=fmmg>{{cite web |url=http://www.filmmusicmag.com/?p=7890 |title=Audio: On The Score With Hans Zimmer |first=Daniel |last=Schweiger |date=2011-05-06 |publisher=Film Music Magazine |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2013-07-19 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130719020043/http://www.filmmusicmag.com/?p=7890 }}</ref>。美国作曲家[[埃里克·惠特克|埃里克·惠特克]]（{{lang|en|Eric Whitacre}}）贡献了多个基于唱诗班的曲段<ref name=fmmg /><ref>{{cite web |last=Whitacre |first=Eric |url=http://ericwhitacre.com/blog/pirates-iv |title=Pirates IV! – Blog |date=2011-01-25 |work=EricWhitacre.com |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2012-09-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120912025746/http://ericwhitacre.com/blog/pirates-iv }}</ref>，多次与季默合作的[[吉奥夫·赞里|吉奥夫·赞里]]（{{lang|en|Geoff Zanelli}}）也参与了电影的作曲工作<ref name=release>{{cite press release |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/walt-disney-pictures-and-jerry-bruckheimer-films-pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-soundtrack-sets-sail-with-oscar-winning-composer-hans-zimmer-at-the-helm-with-acclaimed-guitar-duo-rodrigo-y-gabriela-121486304.html |title=Walt Disney Pictures and Jerry Bruckheimer Films' "Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides" Soundtrack Sets Sail With Oscar®-Winning Composer Hans Zimmer at the Helm With Acclaimed Guitar Duo Rodrigo y Gabriela |publisher=Walt Disney Records |date=2011-05-02 |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2012-10-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121028011249/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/walt-disney-pictures-and-jerry-bruckheimer-films-pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-soundtrack-sets-sail-with-oscar-winning-composer-hans-zimmer-at-the-helm-with-acclaimed-guitar-duo-rodrigo-y-gabriela-121486304.html }}</ref>。

电影的原声带于2011年5月17日发行<ref name="Empiremusic">{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?SID=10279 |title=Pirates Of The Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |publisher=Empire |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2012-03-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323135647/http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?SID=10279 }}</ref>，其中包含18首曲目<ref name="Filmtracks">{{cite web |url=http://www.filmtracks.com/titles/pirates_caribbean4.html |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides (Hans Zimmer Various) |publisher=Filmtracks |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130810021941/http://filmtracks.com/titles/pirates_caribbean4.html |archivedate=2013-08-10 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，全长77分35秒<ref name="Allmusic">{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-mw0002114681 |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides - Hans Zimmer |publisher=Allmusic |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2012-08-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120804025732/http://www.allmusic.com/album/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-mw0002114681 }}</ref>，获得的评价褒贬不一<ref name="moviemusicuk">{{cite web |url=http://moviemusicuk.us/2011/09/07/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-hans-zimmer/ |title=PIRATES OF THE CARIBBEAN: ON STRANGER TIDES – Hans Zimmer |date=2011-09-07 |accessdate=2013-09-13 |publisher=Movie Music HK |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130614114653/http://moviemusicuk.us/2011/09/07/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-hans-zimmer/ |archivedate=2013-06-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="moviewave">{{cite web |url=http://www.movie-wave.net/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides/ |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |author=James Southall |date=2011-05-24 |publisher=Movie Wave |accessdate=2013-11-20 |archivedate=2013-09-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130930213603/http://www.movie-wave.net/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides/ }}</ref><ref name="Tracksounds">{{cite web |url=http://www.tracksounds.com/reviews/pirates_caribbean_stranger_tides_hans_zimmer.htm |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides by Hans Zimmer |accessdate=2013-09-13 |author=Christopher Coleman |publisher=Tracksounds |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427112007/http://www.tracksounds.com/reviews/pirates_caribbean_stranger_tides_hans_zimmer.htm |archivedate=2012-04-27 }}</ref>。

