继[[哥倫比亞電影公司|哥倫比亞電影公司]]宣布推迟[[超凡蜘蛛侠|《蜘蛛侠》重启作品]]发行时间和[[派拉蒙電影公司|派拉蒙電影公司]]宣布《[[雷神_(电影)|雷神]]》将于2011年5月6日上映后，迪士尼于2010年1月6日宣布本片将于2011年5月20日在美国和加拿大上映<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/spider-man-4-release-date-19222 |title='Spider-Man 4' release date squeezed |archivedate=2012-11-03 |first=Carl |last=DiOrio |date=2010-01-06 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103062655/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/spider-man-4-release-date-19222 |accessdate=2013-09-11 }}</ref>。影片通过[[IMAX|IMAX 3D]]、IMAX和传统2D标准进行放映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imax.com/screening/news/IMAX_and_Disney_3_Pic_Deal |title=IMAX and Disney Sign New 3 Picture Deal |publisher=''IMAX Corporation'' |deadurl=yes |date=2010-06-23 |accessdate=2010-07-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100705085514/http://www.imax.com/screening/news/IMAX_and_Disney_3_Pic_Deal |archivedate=2010-07-05 }}</ref><ref name=tron>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=70692 |title=Pirates of the Caribbean Teaser Trailer with TRON: Legacy |publisher=ComingSoon.net |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2012-10-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012001441/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=70692 }}</ref>，采用杜比7.1声道环绕立体声<ref>{{cite news |title='Pirates of the Caribbean,' 'Kung Fu Panda 2' to Use Dolby 7.1 Surround Sound |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/pirates-caribbean-kung-fu-panda-171990 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026114934/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/pirates-caribbean-kung-fu-panda-171990 |archivedate=2012-10-26 |first=Carolyn |last=Giardina |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2011-03-28 |accessdate=2013-09-11 }}</ref>。本片还是第一部在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]和在[[西半球|西半球]]的[[4DX|4DX]]影院放映的电影，其中包括有闪光灯、座位倾斜、刮风、烟雾和气味的特殊效果<ref>{{cite news |last=García Sánchez |first=Rubén |title=Cinépolis presenta sus salas más costosas |url=http://eleconomista.com.mx/entretenimiento/2011/06/02/cinepolis-presenta-sus-salas-mas-costosas |accessdate=2013-09-11 |newspaper=El Economista |date=2011-06-02 |archivedate=2011-08-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110826071314/http://eleconomista.com.mx/entretenimiento/2011/06/02/cinepolis-presenta-sus-salas-mas-costosas }}</ref>。不过只有部分{{lang|en|[[Cinépolis|Cinépolis]]}}电影院独家提供<ref>{{cite news |last=Hecht |first=John |title=Mexico's Cinepolis Going First-class in the U.S. |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/mexicos-cinepolis-going-first-class-208028 |accessdate=2013-11-20 |newspaper=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2011-07-18 |archivedate=2013-11-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131120062723/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/mexicos-cinepolis-going-first-class-208028 }}</ref>。

2011年5月7日，本片在位于加利福尼亚州[[阿納海姆_(加利福尼亞州)|阿纳海姆]]的[[迪士尼樂園|迪士尼樂園]]举行了首映式，这里正是引发该系列电影的加勒比海盗主题公园景点所在地，主演电影的多位明星均有出席。之后还举行了两次早期试映，一次于5月11日在[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]展开<ref>{{cite news |url=http://variety.com/2011/film/news/pirates-set-for-first-russian-bow-1118035965/ |title='Pirates' set for first Russian bow |first=Marc |last=Graser |work=Variety |date=2011-04-27 |accessdate=2013-11-20 |archivedate=2013-11-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131120062636/http://variety.com/2011/film/news/pirates-set-for-first-russian-bow-1118035965/ }}</ref>，另一次则于5月14日在[[戛纳电影节|戛纳电影节]]上进行<ref name=EW.com>{{cite news |last=Breznican |first=Anthony |title=Johnny Depp's 'Pirates 4' headed for Cannes Film Festival |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/04/13/johnny-depps-pirates-4-headed-for-cannes-film-festival/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60niMcvya?url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/04/13/johnny-depps-pirates-4-headed-for-cannes-film-festival |archivedate=2011-08-09 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |newspaper=Entertainment Weekly |date=2011-04-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。电影在世界各国的开映日期是5月18至20日，其中英国为5月18日，澳大利亚为5月19日，北美是5月20日<ref>{{cite web |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |url=http://www.ign.com/movies/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides/theater-859550 |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2012-11-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107155649/http://www.ign.com/movies/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides/theater-859550 }}</ref><ref name="Coming Soon">{{cite news |last=Lesnick |first=Silas |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides Teaser Shown Read more: UPDATE: Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides Teaser Shown |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=68177 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |newspaper=Coming Soon |date=2010-07-22 |archivedate=2013-04-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130412094844/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=68177 }}</ref><ref name="OK Magazine">{{cite news |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |url=http://www.okmagazine.com.au/entertainment/238-pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides.htm |accessdate=2013-09-11 |newspaper=OK Magazine Australia |date=2011-01-25 |archivedate=2012-04-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401222059/http://www.okmagazine.com.au/entertainment/238-pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides.htm }}</ref><ref name=IMAX>{{cite web |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides An IMAX 3D Experience |url=http://www.imax.com/movies/m/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-an-imax-3d-experience/ |work=IMAX.com |publisher=IMAX |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2012-10-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121030093403/http://www.imax.com/movies/m/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-an-imax-3d-experience/ }}</ref>。

