===促销===
迪士尼的营销总监[[M·T·卡尼|M·T·卡尼]]（{{lang|en|M. T. Carney}}）表示，电影的广告活动旨在“提醒人们为什么他们一开始会喜欢杰克·斯派罗，并且以一种高雅的方式引入新的元素”<ref name="making2" />。[[索尼影視娛樂|索尼影視娛樂]]前市场总监瓦莱丽·凡·加尔德（{{lang|en|Valerie Van Galder}}）获聘担任顾问<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/09/08/us-disney-idUSTRE6870ON20100908 |first=Kim |last=Masters |title=Disney hires new marketing guru for "Pirates 4" |work=The Hollywood Reporter |publisher=Reuters |date=2010-09-08 |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2012-10-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022210236/http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/09/08/us-disney-idUSTRE6870ON20100908 }}</ref>。电影的第一个片段出现在2010年12月4日的[[电视节目|电视节目]]《[[娱乐今宵|娱乐今宵]]》（{{lang|en|Entertainment Tonight}}）上<ref>{{cite web |first=Jordan |last=Raup |url=http://thefilmstage.com/news/first-footage-from-pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides/ |script-title=en:First Footage From ‘Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides’ |date=2010-12-05 |work=The Film Stage |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2012-07-31 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120731142607/http://thefilmstage.com/news/first-footage-from-pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides/ }}</ref>。影片先后发行了三段预告片<ref name=making2 />，一部为3D版本，于12月和《[[創：光速戰記|創：光速戰記]]》一起发映<ref name=tron />，并在{{lang|en|ESPN 3D}}电视台播出<ref name="Media Post">{{cite news |last=Goetzel |first=David |title=ESPN Airs 3D Ads, Movie Trailers |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101217152021/http://www.mediapost.com/publications/?fa=Articles.showArticle&art_aid=141400 |archivedate=2010-12-17 |url=http://www.mediapost.com/publications/?fa=Articles.showArticle&art_aid=141400 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2011-04-21 |newspaper=Media Post |date=2010-12-15 }}</ref>；另一部于2011年2月在[[第四十五届超级碗|第四十五届超级碗]]广告中播出，之后再以加长版形式在线上发布<ref name="Latino Review 3">{{cite news |last=Lichtig |first=Max |title='Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides' Super Bowl Spot |archivedate=2012-09-02 |deadurl=no |url=http://collider.com/pirates-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-super-bowl-ad/74930/ |accessdate=2013-09-13 |publisher=Collider |date=2011-02-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120902032554/http://collider.com/pirates-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-super-bowl-ad/74930 }}</ref>；最后一段预告片于3月发布，与之前的预告片和广告相比，这一预告片包含更多剧情内容<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hitfix.com/blogs/motion-captured/posts/disney-spills-even-more-story-details-in-new-pirates-4-trailer |first=Drew |last=McWeeny |title=Disney spills even more story details in new 'Pirates 4' trailer and stills |date=2011-03-21 |work=HitFix |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2012-05-31 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531074429/http://www.hitfix.com/blogs/motion-captured/posts/disney-spills-even-more-story-details-in-new-pirates-4-trailer }}</ref>。

