sher=Pirate Brands |date=2011-05-02 |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2011-08-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110823110319/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20110502005972/en/Pirate%E2%80%99s-Booty-Collaborates-Disney%27s-%22Pirates-Caribbean-Stranger }}</ref>，还有由{{lang|en|OPI}}开发的指甲油产品线<ref>{{cite web |url=http://corporate.disney.go.com/corporate/moreinfo/poc_toys.html |title=Discover a Treasure Trove of Color with New BRIGHTS by OPI, Inspired by Disney and Jerry Bruckheimer Film's Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |publisher=Walt Disney Corporation |accessdate=2012-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120110035854/http://corporate.disney.go.com/corporate/moreinfo/poc_toys.html |archivedate=2012-01-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，{{lang|en|Hot Topic}}（意译为“热门主题”）的服装<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2013-09-13 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20110509006021/en |title=Disney and Hot Topic Present Treasure-Filled "Pirates Day" Fan Events to Celebrate Walt Disney Pictures and Jerry Bruckheimer Films' "Pirates of the Caribbean: on Stranger Tides" |publisher=Business Wire |date=2011-05-09 |accessdate=2013-11-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130913070152/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20110509006021/en }}</ref>和[[施华洛世奇|施华洛世奇]]的珠宝<ref>{{cite web |title=Swarovski – Swarovski's Collaboration with Disney Continues with "Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides" Collection |archivedate=2012-03-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328111015/http://www.brand.swarovski.com/Content.Node/presscentre/news/news-jewelry/piratesofthecaribbean.en.html#/en/presscentre/news/news-jewelry/piratesofthecaribbean |url=http://www.brand.swarovski.com/Content.Node/presscentre/news/news-jewelry/piratesofthecaribbean.en.html#/en/presscentre/news/news-jewelry/piratesofthecaribbean |date=2010-12-10 |publisher=Swarovski |accessdate=2013-09-13 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|Goldline}}国际（{{lang|en|Goldline International}}）推出了电影中[[西班牙銀圓|西班牙銀圓]]的复制品和一些金币，用来在一家剧院进行抽奖活动<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goldline.com/disney-movie-giveaway/ |title=Goldline Coin Giveaway |publisher=Goldline International |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2012-06-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120611013338/http://www.goldline.com/disney-movie-giveaway/ }}</ref>。在[[迪士尼加州冒險樂園|迪士尼加州冒險樂園]]，《[[缤纷世界|缤纷世界]]》（{{lang|en|World of Color}}）演出的《加勒比海盗》部分有所延长，其中包括了本片中的一些视频和音乐片段<ref>{{cite web |title=Disney's magic undergoes changes |work=The Press-Enterprise |date=2011-06-09 |accessdate=2013-11-20 |first=Timothy |last=Guy |url=http://www.pe.com/local-news/local-news-headlines/20110610-disneys-magic-undergoes-changes.ece |archivedate=2013-11-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131120063827/http://www.pe.com/local-news/local-news-headlines/20110610-disneys-magic-undergoes-changes.ece }}</ref>。

