chive-chart/_/26/2011-10-01/ |title=TOP 40 DVD ARCHIVE 1st October 2011 |publisher=The Official Charts Company |accessdate=2013-11-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911151313/http://www.officialcharts.com/video-archive-chart/_/26/2011-10-01/ |archivedate=2013-09-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2011年12月6日，影片面向美国和[[加拿大|加拿大]]发行了高清家用格式，一共有3种不同的套装可供选择，一种两碟装（一张蓝光，一张DVD），一种五碟装（两张蓝光，一张蓝光{{lang|en|3D}}，一张{{lang|en|DVD}}，一张数字副本），还有一种是包括了全部4部加勒比海盗系列电影的15碟珍藏版套装。此外影片还提供了高清和{{lang|en|3D}}格式在线下载<ref name="ET Online">{{cite news |title=Exclusive Clip: 'Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides' Mermaid Magic |url=http://www.etonline.com/movies/112349_Exclusive_Clip_Pirates_of_the_Caribbean_On_Stranger_Tides_Mermaid_Magic/index.html |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2012-09-26 |deadurl=yes |work=Entertainment Tonight |date=2011-07-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120926021855/http://www.etonline.com/movies/112349_Exclusive_Clip_Pirates_of_the_Caribbean_On_Stranger_Tides_Mermaid_Magic/index.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Smith |first=Matthew |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides Blu-ray and Blu-ray 3D |url=http://www.blu-ray.com/news/?id=6864 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |publisher=Blu-Ray.com |date=2011-07-14 |archivedate=2012-04-06 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406172340/http://www.blu-ray.com/news/?id=6864 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=McCutcheon |first=David |title=Pirates' Stranger Tides Revealed |url=http://dvd.ign.com/articles/118/1182102p1.html |accessdate=2012-06-03 |publisher=Blu-Ray.com |date=2011-07-14 |archivedate=2012-06-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120603023240/http://dvd.ign.com/articles/118/1182102p1.html }}</ref>。而普通DVD的版本则于12月6日发行<ref>{{cite news |last=Grabert |first=Jessica |title=Disney Will Delay Pirates Of The Caribbean DVD For A Month After Blu-Ray |url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Disney-Will-Delay-Pirates-Of-The-Caribbean-DVD-For-A-Month-After-Blu-Ray-25716.html |accessdate=2013-09-11 |publisher=Cinema Blend |date=2011-07-15 |archivedate=2012-10-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017210512/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Disney-Will-Delay-Pirates-Of-The-Caribbean-DVD-For-A-Month-After-Blu-Ray-25716.html }}</ref>。

