== 迴響 ==
=== 票房 ===
《加勒比海盗4：惊涛怪浪》在北美收入{{lang|en|2}}亿{{lang|en|4107}}万{{lang|en|1802}}美元票房，其他国家8亿零280万美元，总计{{lang|en|10}}亿{{lang|en|4387}}万{{lang|en|1802}}美元<ref name="mojopotc4" />，是2011年的世界电影票房[[季军|季军]]（仅次于《[[哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）|哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）]]》和《[[變形金剛3|變形金剛3]]》），也是加勒比海盗系列电影中第二卖座的作品。截止2019年7月，影片仍然可以在世界电影历史票房总榜上[[最高電影票房收入列表|名列第31位]]<ref name="worldwide">{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/ |title=WORLDWIDE GROSSES |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130726070111/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/ |archivedate=2013-07-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，也可以在华特迪士尼电影公司发行过的所有电影中排到第17位<ref name="worldwide" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/?pagenum=1&sort=studio&order=ASC&p=.htm |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |title=All Time Worldwide Box Office Grosses |archive-date=2013-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130907012718/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/?pagenum=1&sort=studio&order=ASC&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。电影在世界各国上映首周的票房总和达到3.5亿美元，超过《加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头》创下的本系列3.44亿美元的纪录，并且可以在历史上所有电影的同一项目成绩中排到第20位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/worldwideopenings.htm |title=WORLDWIDE OPENINGS |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-08-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130801031300/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/worldwideopenings.htm }}</ref>。影片还创下了[[IMAX|IMAX]]院线全球上映首周收入{{lang|en|1670}}万美元的纪录<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/pirates-box-office-opens-3464-191018 |script-title=en:Box Office Report: Disney’s ‘Pirates’ $346 million Opening Fourth Biggest Worldwide Debut Ever |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2011-05-22 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |first=Pamela |last=McClintock |archivedate=2012-11-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103062950/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/pirates-box-office-opens-3464-191018 }}</ref>，不过这个纪录不久就被《變形金剛3》打破<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-transformers-dark-207883 |title=Box Office Report: 'Transformers: Dark of the Moon' Scores Third-Best Global Bow Ever |date=2011-07-03 |first=Pamela |last=McClintock |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2012-11-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102222050/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-transformers-dark-207883 }}</ref>。

电影分别用10、12和16天达到了5亿、6亿和7亿美元的全球票房，这都刷新了以最快速度达到这一目标的纪录<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-warner-bros-192776 |title=Friday Box Office: 'Hangover 2' No. 1 With $30 Mil |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |first=Pamela |last=McClintock |date=2011-05-27 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2012-11-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103063028/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-warner-bros-192776 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3176&p=.htm |title=Around-the-World Brief: 'Pirates' Booty Grows, 'Hangover,' 'Panda' Sequels Open Strongly |publisher=Box Office Mojo |first=Gray |last=Brandon |date=2011-05-29 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511161846/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3176&p=.htm }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-pirates-caribbean-194751 |title=Box Office Report: 'Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides' Sails Past $700 Mil Mark |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |first=Pamela |last=McClintock |date=2011-06-03 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2012-11-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103063339/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-pirates-caribbean-194751 }}</ref>。不过其中5亿的纪录被《变形金刚3》超越<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3203&p=.htm |title='Transformers' Blowing Up Worldwide Records |publisher=Box Office Mojo |first=Subers |last=Ray |date=2011-07-08 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514220603/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3203&p=.htm |deadurl=no }}</ref>，另外两个也被同年的《哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）》超越<ref name="boxofficemojo1">{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3222&p=.htm |title=Around-the-World Roundup: 'Potter' Still Magic Overseas |publisher=Box Office Mojo |first=Subers |last=Ray |date=2011-07-26 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511162929/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3222&p=.htm |deadurl=no }}</ref>。在电影院上遇46天后（{{lang|en|2011}}年7月2日），本片成为历史上第8部，也是华特迪士尼公司发行的第4位票房超过10亿美元的电影<ref name="Reuters1G">{{cite news |title="Pirates" treasure mounts to $1 billion worldwide |publisher=Reuters |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/07/02/us-pirates-idUSTRE7611NC20110702 |date=2011-07-02 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130701182712/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/07/02/us-pirates-idUSTRE7611NC20110702 |archivedate=2013-07-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，并创下迪士尼公司出口电影中以最快速度达到这一目标的新纪录（这项纪录保持了近一年后被《[[復仇者聯盟_(電影)|復仇者聯盟]]》超越）<ref name="Time-1billion">{{cite news |last=Corliss |first=Richard |title=The Avengers Storms the Billion Dollar Club — In Just 19 Days |archivedate=2013-05-21 |deadurl=no |url=http://entertainment.time.com/2012/05/13/the-avengers-storms-the-billion-dollar-club-in-just-19-days/ |accessdate=2013-09-11 |newspaper=Time |date=2012-05-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130521165524/http://entertainment.time.com/2012/05/13/the-avengers-storms-the-billion-dollar-club-in-just-19-days/ }}</ref>，这个速度当时也可以在所有电影中排到第5位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3234&p=.htm |title='Transformers' Becomes Tenth Billion-Dollar Movie Ever; 'Potter' Hits Another Worldwide Milestone |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130516023415/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3234&p=.htm |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

====北美====
《加勒比海盗4：惊涛怪浪》于[[星期四|星期四]]午夜场开始在北美{{lang|en|2210}}家电影院放映，该午夜场共计收入{{lang|en|470}}万美元<ref>{{cite news |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3166&p=.htm |title=Forecast: 'Pirates' Has Some Life Left in It |publisher=Box Office Mojo |date=2011-05-20 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512065142/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3166&p=.htm }}</ref>，首映当天一共收入{{lang|en|3486}}万零{{lang|en|549}}美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=daily&id=piratesofthecaribbean4.htm |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510224313/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=daily&id=piratesofthecaribbean4.htm |archivedate=2013-05-10 }}</ref>。影片上映首周进账{{lang|en|9015}}万{{lang|en|1958}}美元，登上周票房榜[[冠军|冠军]]宝座，但与两部前作《加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头》（{{lang|en|1.147}}亿）和《加勒比海盗2：聚魂棺》（{{lang|en|1.356}}亿）相比均有不及，也比不上之前一年约翰尼·德普主演的《[[魔境夢遊|魔境夢遊]]》（{{lang|en|1.161}}亿）<ref>{{cite news |title=Weekend Report: 'Pirates' Rides Smaller 'Tides' |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3169&p=.htm |publisher=Box Office Mojo |first=Brandon |last=Gray |date=2011-05-23 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511161408/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3169&p=.htm }}</ref>。其中3D放映的收入仅占首周票房的{{lang|en|46%}}<ref name=3DEW>{{cite web |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/05/25/pirates-caribbean-stranger-tides-3d-box-office/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526145820/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/05/25/pirates-caribbean-stranger-tides-3d-box-office/ |archivedate=2013-05-26 |title='Pirates of the Caribbean': Why didn't more American moviegoers opt to see Jack Sparrow in 3-D? |work=Entertainment Weekly |first=John |last=Young |accessdate=2013-09-11 |date=2011-05-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。电影放映于2011年9月29日结束，共计收入为{{lang|en|2}}亿{{lang|en|4107}}万{{lang|en|1802}}美元，可以在{{lang|en|2011}}年的电影票房排列榜上名列第5位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2011&p=.htm |title=2011 DOMESTIC GROSSES |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501035921/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2011&p=.htm }}</ref>，是加勒比海盗系列中收益最少的作品<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=piratesofthecaribbean.htm |title=Pirates of the Caribbean Movies at the Box Office |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130425023334/http://boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=piratesofthecaribbean.htm |archivedate=2013-04-25 }}</ref>。不过，影片也以{{lang|en|1.668}}亿美元的成绩，名列{{lang|en|2011}}年5月的北美票房榜首位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3181&p=.htm |title=May Posts Record Gross |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511214320/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3181&p=.htm }}</ref>。

====北美以外地区====
截止2019年7月，《加勒比海盗4：惊涛怪浪》仍然可以在北美以外国家电影总票房排行榜上名列第19位<ref name="worldnonm">{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/?pagenum=1&sort=osgross&order=DESC&p=.htm |title=All Time Worldwide Box Office Grosses |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archive-date=2013-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510005915/http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/?pagenum=1&sort=osgross&order=DESC&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在所有迪士尼公司出品电影中则名列第8位<ref name="worldnonm" /><ref name="hollywoodreporter.com">{{cite news |title=Box Office Shocker: 'Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides' Is Disney's Top Film of All Time Overseas |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-shocker-pirates-caribbean-202030 |archivedate=2012-11-09 |deadurl=no |date=2011-06-15 |accessdate=2011-06-16 |first=Pamela |last=McClintock |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109183734/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-shocker-pirates-caribbean-202030 }}</ref>，是2011年的北美以外国家电影总票房冠军，也是加勒比海盗系列电影在这些国家总票房最高的一部<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/weekend/yearly/?yr=2011&p=.htm |title=2011 Overseas Total Yearly Box Office Results |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2012-11-19 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121119075532/http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/weekend/yearly/?yr=2011&p=.htm }}</ref>。并且是至少58个国家和地区最卖座的一部加勒比海盗系列电影<ref name="Reuters1G" />。

2011年5月18日（[[星期三|星期三]]），影片开始在10个国家和地区上映，这一天一共收入了{{lang|en|1850}}万美元<ref name="The Hollywood Reporter">{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/pirates-caribbean-earns-185-million-190286 |title='Pirates of the Caribbean' Earns $18.5 Million Internationally |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2011-05-19 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |first=Frank |last=Segers |archivedate=2012-11-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103063715/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/pirates-caribbean-earns-185-million-190286 }}</ref>，次日上映国家和地区又增加了37个，共计收入{{lang|en|2570}}万美元，将总票房提高到{{lang|en|4420}}万美元<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/pirates-caribbean-opens-47-million-190672 |title='Pirates of the Caribbean' Opens to $4.7 Million at Midnight Showings |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2011-05-20 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |first=Pamela |last=McClintock |archivedate=2012-11-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103063846/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/pirates-caribbean-opens-47-million-190672 }}</ref>，到了[[星期五|星期五]]，上映国家数量进一步扩张，收入达到{{lang|en|4620}}万美元，3天共计{{lang|en|9210}}万美元<ref>{{cite news |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3167&p=.htm |title='Pirates' Already Making Waves Overseas |publisher=Box Office Mojo |date=2011-05-20 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515105240/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3167&p=.htm }}</ref>。电影前5天一共在超过{{lang|en|100}}个国家和地区的约{{lang|en|18210}}张银幕上发映，创下了收入2.6亿美元的新纪录，并且在这{{lang|en|100}}多个国家和地区都登上了票房榜冠军的位置<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&view=byweekend&id=piratesofthecaribbean4.htm |title=PIRATES OF THE CARIBBEAN: ON STRANGER TIDES |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2012-10-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023072001/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&view=byweekend&id=piratesofthecaribbean4.htm |deadurl=no }}</ref>。不过，这个纪录之后不久就被《哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）》打破<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/weekend/opening/ |title=OVERSEAS TOTAL ALL TIME OPENINGS |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508201519/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/intl/weekend/opening/ }}</ref>。这些国家和地区首周3D放映的收入占总收入的{{lang|en|66%}}，远远超过在北美的表现<ref name=3DEW />。影片第一周在[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]和[[独联体|独联体]]国家收入了{{lang|en|3142}}万美元（包括预映），是除北美外所有国家中最高的<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/intl/cis/?yr=2011&wk=20&p=new |title=Russia - CIS Box Office May 19–22, 2011 |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305210208/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/intl/cis/?yr=2011&wk=20&p=new |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]以{{lang|en|2295}}万美元的成绩紧随其后<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficefollower.net/2011/05/china-weekly-box-office-516-522.html |title=China Weekly Box Office (5/16 - 5/22): Hollywood films continue to dominate as Pirates 4 claimed the biggest opening of the year |publisher=Box Office Follower |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2012-04-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426082438/http://www.boxofficefollower.net/2011/05/china-weekly-box-office-516-522.html }}</ref>，收入{{lang|en|2053}}万美元的[[德国|德国]]名列第3位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/intl/germany/?yr=2011&wk=20&p=.htm |title=Germany Box Office May 19–22, 2011 |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2011-11-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111114165102/http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/germany/?yr=2011&wk=20&p=.htm }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3170&p=.htm |title=Around-the-World Roundup: 'Pirates' Sails to New Overseas Record |publisher=Box Office Mojo |date=2011-05-22 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-12 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512062023/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3170&p=.htm }}</ref>。虽然有来自《[[宿醉2|宿醉2]]》、《[[功夫熊猫2|功夫熊猫2]]》和《[[X战警：第一战|X战警：第一战]]》的竞争，但影片还是成功霸占海外国家票房冠军位置3个星期<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3176&p=.htm |title=Around-the-World Brief: 'Pirates' Booty Grows, 'Hangover,' 'Panda' Sequels Open Strongly |publisher=Box Office Mojo |first=Gray |last=Brandon |date=2011-05-31 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511161846/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3176&p=.htm }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3180&p=.htm |title=Around-the-World Brief: 'Pirates' Out-Class 'X-Men' |publisher=Box Office Mojo |first=Brandon |last=Gray |date=2011-06-05 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-05-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512205004/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3180&p=.htm |deadurl=no }}</ref>。影片以7、11、14天的速度分别在海外市场达到3亿、4亿和5亿美元的目标，创下新的纪录，这个纪录之后也被《哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）》超越<ref name="Reuters1G" /><ref name="boxofficemojo1"/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/disneys-pirates-caribbean-hits-400-192291 |title=Disney's 'Pirates of the Caribbean' Hits $400 Million Worldwide in Less Than a Week |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2011-05-25 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |first=Pamela |last=McClintock |archivedate=2012-09-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120904095108/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/disneys-pirates-caribbean-hits-400-192291 }}</ref>。

《加勒比海盗4：惊涛怪浪》创下了俄罗斯（包括独联体国家）和[[瑞典|瑞典]]的上映首日票房新纪录<ref name="The Hollywood Reporter" />，之后还分别在[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]、[[中东|中东]]、俄罗斯、[[挪威|挪威]]、[[乌克兰|乌克兰]]和[[土耳其|土耳其]]创下了首周票房新纪录<ref name="overseas"/>，其中俄罗斯（2675万3256美元）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/cis/opening/ |title=RUSSIA - CIS ALL TIME OPENINGS |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515145130/http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/cis/opening/ |archivedate=2013-05-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>、乌克兰（215万4010美元）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/ukraine/opening/ |title=UKRAINE ALL TIME OPENINGS |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515152933/http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/ukraine/opening/ |archivedate=2013-05-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>的纪录截止2013年9月11日仍然保持。除北美外，影片在日本获得的收益最高，达1.089亿美元，其次是收入7180万美元的中华人民共和国<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/christian-bale-flowers-of-war-dark-knight-china-box-office-277004 |title=Box Office Report: Christian Bale's 'Flowers of War' Already Top-Grossing Chinese Film of 2011 |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2011-12-30 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |first=Pamela |last=McClintock |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120909135916/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/christian-bale-flowers-of-war-dark-knight-china-box-office-277004 |archivedate=2012-09-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，接下来是俄罗斯和独联体国家（6366万1354美元）<ref name="POTC4-overseas">{{cite web |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides (2011) - International Box Office Results |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=piratesofthecaribbean4.htm |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-11 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-05-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515033111/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=piratesofthecaribbean4.htm }}</ref>。此外，本片也是2011年俄罗斯和独联体国家<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/cis/yearly/?yr=2011&p=.htm |title=Russia - CIS Yearly 