=== 专业评价 ===
《加勒比海盗4：惊涛怪浪》所获得的专业评价以负面为主。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的266篇评论文章，其中只有85篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为32%，平均得分5（最高为10）。网站的共识评价写道：“和以往的续集相比，本作更短小精悍，但这个“海盗”还是有着脱节的故事情节、嘈杂的动作桥段和永无休止的攻势。”<ref name="Rotten Tomatoes">{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pirates_of_the_caribbean_on_stranger_tides/ |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides Reviews |work=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Flixster |accessdate=2013-09-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822212732/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pirates_of_the_caribbean_on_stranger_tides/ |archivedate=2013-08-22 }}</ref>。而从{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}上收集的39份评价来看，其中11篇给出好评，7篇差评，21篇褒贬不一，[[加權平均數|加權平均數]]为45（最高100）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |work=Metacritic |publisher=CBS |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2012-11-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114155511/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]}}（意译为“电影评分”）针对影迷进行的一次调查结果显示电影获得了{{lang|en|B+}}的评级（最高为A+，最低为F）<ref name=naopening/>。

[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]给予影片两星的评价（最高四星），认为以佩内洛普·克鲁兹代替凯拉·奈特利和奥兰多·布鲁姆虽然有正面的效果，但在他看来总体上还是“太大同小异了”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-2011 |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |author=Ebert, Roger |work=Chicago Sun-Times |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-06-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608024307/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-2011 }}</ref>。《[[底特律新闻|底特律新闻]]》（{{lang|en|The Detroit News}}）的汤姆·隆（{{lang|en|Tom Long}}）给予本片{{lang|en|D+}}的评价，称杰克·斯派罗的受欢迎程度已经耗尽。虽然影片在剧情上更流畅，但“这部电影还是太荒谬了”。他认为从一系列根据一个主题公园景点改编的电影来说，《加勒比海盗4：惊涛怪浪》作为其第4部作品的表现正如所预料的那样，充满了大量的噪音，大把的特技和彻头彻尾的愚蠢内容<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mysanantonio.com/entertainment/movies/article/Pirates-movie-makes-little-sense-but-a-lot-of-1395647.php |title=Review: Fourth 'Pirates' movie makes little sense but a lot of noise |first=Tom |last=Long |work=San Antonio Express-News |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archive-date=2015-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150604081408/http://www.mysanantonio.com/entertainment/movies/article/Pirates-movie-makes-little-sense-but-a-lot-of-1395647.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。英国影评人[[马克·克默德|马克·克默德]]（{{lang|en|Mark Kermode}}）在自己的节目上给予本片彻底的负面评价，称“这不是什么第三方的惊人误判，因为这什么都不是，这就是一大片虚无，在身为第三方的我看来，这就什么都不是”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-13475908 |title=Mark Kermode savages new Pirates Of The Caribbean film |work=BBC |date=2011-05-20 |accessdate=2013-09-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110821022658/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-13475908 |archivedate=2011-08-21 }}</ref>。

与之前的作品一样，本片也受到了剧情欠连贯和混乱的批评。《[[亚利桑那共和|亚利桑那共和]]》（{{lang|en|The Arizona Republic}}）影评人比尔·古迪库恩兹（{{lang|en|Bill Goodykoontz}}）给电影的评分为2（最高为5），称“这部电影就是把一系列杂乱无章的内容扔到一块，希望他们会自己拼凑成一个连贯的故事，（但）这样的事情从来都没发生过”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.azcentral.com/thingstodo/movies/articles/2011/05/18/20110518review-pirates-caribbean-stranger-tides-goodykoontz.html |title='Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides,' 2 stars |first=Bill |last=Goodykoontz |work=The Arizona Republic |date=2011-05-18 |accessdate=2013-09-11}}</ref>。在线影评人[[詹姆斯·伯拉迪尼|詹姆斯·伯拉迪尼]]（{{lang|en|James Berardinelli}}）认为影片的剧本比一根晃来晃去的晾衣绳强不了多少<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reelviews.net/php_review_template.php?identifier=2311 |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |author=Berardinelli, James |date=2011-05-19 |work=Reelviews |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-04-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130403074520/http://www.reelviews.net/php_review_template.php?identifier=2311 }}</ref>，《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》的克劳迪娅·普格（{{lang|en|Claudia Puig}}）觉得这是一部“熟悉且可预料”的电影，情节“经常脱节并且堆砌了大量毫无意义的细节”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2011-05-27-On-Stranger-Tides-movie-review_n.htm |title='Pirates: On Stranger Tides' in precarious position |first=Claudia |last=Puig |date=2011-05-19 |work=USA Today |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archive-date=2012-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121207172927/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2011-05-27-On-Stranger-Tides-movie-review_n.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《[[时代花絮报|时代花絮报]]》（{{lang|en|The Times-Picayune}}）的麦克·斯科特（{{lang|en|Mike Scott}}）认为本片与首部作品相比虽然有所不久，但已经足以弥补第三部电影中的大部分愚蠢的失误<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2011/05/pirates_of_the_caribbean_on_st.html |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |first=Mike |last=Scott |date=2011-05-20 |work=The Times-Picayune |accessdate=2013-09-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511213119/http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2011/05/pirates_of_the_caribbean_on_st.html |archivedate=2013-05-11 }}</ref>。[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]的塔莎·罗宾逊（{{lang|en|Tasha Robinson}}）形容本片在“设计和必要性上比之前的电影的规模要小”，觉得“这个系列需要这样的精简”，因为对电影来说，“轻巧总好过臃肿”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.avclub.com/articles/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides,56276/ |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |first=Tasha |last=Robinson |date=2011-05-19 |work=The A.V. Club |archivedate=2012-08-15 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120815122533/http://www.avclub.com/articles/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides%2C56276/ }}</ref>。

当然，影片也有获得较为正面的评价，一些影评人认为本片制作精良，并且很有娱乐性。理查德·罗伯（{{lang|en|Richard Roeper}}）给予B+的评级，形容这是“自首部后最有趣的一部作品”，他称电影的故事情节“纯粹是动画片，比另外几部续集易懂多了”，最终的总结认为“这个系列已经开始让人厌倦，但佩内洛普为其注入了新的能量”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.richardroeper.com/reviews/piratesofthecaribbeanonstrangertides.aspx#share |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |publisher=ReelzChannel |author=Roeper, Richard |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2013-05-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501170923/http://www.richardroeper.com/reviews/piratesofthecaribbeanonstrangertides.aspx#share }}</ref>。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的安·霍纳迪（{{lang|en|Ann Hornaday}}）也有同样的看法，并给予影片三星的评价（最高四星），称赞影片给人带来了“新鲜和振奋的感觉”。她称赞马歇尔“迅速且有条不紊地提供了连串的动作戏，表现出令人瞠目的逃避主义思想”，还表扬了德普、克鲁兹和麦柯肖恩的表演<ref name="Barker">{{cite news |url=http://variety.com/2011/film/reviews/pirates-of-the-caribbean-on-stranger-tides-1117945199/ |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides |first=Andrew |last=Barker |date=2011-05-12 |work=Variety |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2012-07-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120717051528/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117945199?refcatid=31 }}</ref>。《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》的雷·贝内特（{{lang|en|Ray Bennett}}）对佩内洛普·克鲁兹的角色表示欢迎，称她“带来了她获奥斯卡金像奖的活力”，还与德普间有着“生动的性张力”，并认为马歇尔“在所有常见的追逐和斗剑戏码上表现出了不起的天赋，而且对3D的处理也很出色”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/pirates-caribbean-stranger-tides/review/186896 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60nhWdjZN?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/pirates-caribbean-stranger-tides-review-186896 |archivedate=2011-08-09 |title=Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides: Review |first=Ray |last=Bennett |date=2011-05-10 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=2013-09-13 }}</ref>。《[[环球邮报|环球邮报]]》的里克·葛瑞恩（{{lang|en|Rick Groen}}）认为部分动作场面仍有些杂乱，但对总体效果感到满意，他称麦柯肖恩是个“令人耳目一新的恶棍”，他那“宏亮的音调在任何地方都能受到欢迎”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/film/pirates-of-the-caribbean-4-ahoy-me-hearties-theres-treasure-amid-the-bloat/article628879/ |title=Pirates of the Caribbean 4: Ahoy me hearties, there’s treasure amid the bloat |first=Rick |last=Groen |date=2011-05-20 |work=The Globe and Mail |accessdate=2013-09-13 |location=Toronto |archivedate=2013-07-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724035034/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/film/pirates-of-the-caribbean-4-ahoy-me-hearties-theres-treasure-amid-the-bloat/article628879/ }}</ref>。《[[综艺|综艺]]》的安德鲁·巴克（{{lang|en|Andrew Barker}}）认为电影还算可以接受，其中有些原创性，但还没有多大意义。他称赞了杰弗里·拉什的表现，称他不但演绎了最好笑的台词和镜头，而且也开始表现出原本只属于德普的那种流氓般的魅力<ref name="Barker" />。

===荣誉===
《加勒比海盗4：惊涛怪浪》获得了4项[[青少年选择奖|青少年选择奖]]提名，分别是科幻/奇幻类电影、科幻/奇幻类男演员、科幻/奇幻类女演员和电影恶棍<ref name=tca2011>{{cite web |url=http://www.eonline.com/news/249838/teen-choice-awards-nominees-announced-it-s-a-harry-potter-vs-twilight-showdown |title=Teen Choice Awards Nominees Announced |publisher=E! Online |date=2011-06-29 |accessdate=2013-09-13 |author=Garvey, Marianne |archivedate=2012-10-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021041006/http://www.eonline.com/news/249838/teen-choice-awards-nominees-announced-it-s-a-harry-potter-vs-twilight-showdown }}</ref>。电影的预告片和电视广告获得了[[金拖车奖|金拖车奖]]（{{lang|en|Golden Trailer Awards}}）提名<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.prweb.com/releases/2011/6/prweb8526484.htm | title=The 12th Annual Golden Trailer Awards® Posts Nominations for Best Movie Promos of 2011: Live Gala Award Show Will be Held June 29 at the Music Box Theatre in L.A. | publisher=Golden Trailer Awards.com | date=2011-06-03 | accessdate=2011-06-18 | archive-date=2011-06-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607042507/http://www.prweb.com/releases/2011/6/prweb8526484.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。山姆·克拉弗林获得了帝国奖最佳男新人奖提名，约翰尼·德普还获得了[[尼克频道儿童选择奖|尼克频道儿童选择奖]]最受欢迎男演员奖提名，而汉斯·季默得到了[[美国作曲家、作家和发行商协会|美国作曲家、作家和发行商协会]]的肯定<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1298650/awards |title=Awards for Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides (2011) |work=IMDb |publisher=Amazon |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2012-04-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120404001415/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1298650/awards }}</ref>。

