}}</ref>。於2016年又宣布延期至2017年7月7日於美國上映<ref name="2017 release">{{cite news |last=Lang |first=Brent |title='Pirates of the Caribbean 5' to Hit Theaters July 2017 |url=https://variety.com/2014/film/news/pirates-of-the-caribbean-5-to-hit-theaters-in-july-2017-1201267477/ |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2014-07-23 |accessdate=2014-07-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140725100544/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/pirates-of-the-caribbean-5-to-hit-theaters-in-july-2017-1201267477/ |archivedate=2014-07-25 }}</ref>，最終美國檔期訂於2017年5月26日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/pirates-caribbean-5-world-premiere-at-shanghai-disneyland-997583 |title=Pirates of the Caribbean 5' to World Premiere at Shanghai Disneyland |author=Patrick Brzeski |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2017-04-25 |accessdate=2017-04-25 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170426032742/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/pirates-caribbean-5-world-premiere-at-shanghai-disneyland-997583 |archivedate=2017-04-26 }}</ref>。

